originalText.text: I had the pleasure of meeting Dr. Rapoport in early 2020 after seeing another neurologist. Dr. Rapaport gave me the most thorough exam I ever had in my life, asked a lot of questions, and also reviewed my MRI scan as well as the report. He spent the time reviewing it all and then proceeded to explain what he thought was going on with me and what I should expect in terms of recovery. He answered all of my questions and believe me I had a ton. His diagnosis was spot on. The man is beyond brilliant and I am forever grateful our paths have crossed. Thank you, Dr. Rapoport!!
